B. Discuss with stakeholder and determine which project close and which add&lt;br /&gt;
C. Discuss with sponsor and ask sponsor to decide which project close and which add&lt;br /&gt;
D. Submit change request to GB to decide which project close and which add, and reassign some resource&lt;/p&gt;
