&lt;h4 id=&#34;66-the-program-manager-updates-the-stakeholders-register-and-sends-the-program-scope-statement-to-the-legal-adviser-for-review-the-legal-adviser-recommends-several-changes-the-program-manager-meets-with-stakeholders-from-marketing-finance-and-operations-to-discuss-the-changes-and-obtain-approvals-these-stakeholders-believe-that-the-changes-will-diminish-the-products-value-and-affect-profitability-what-must-be-updated-and-acted-upon-to-ensure-the-program-does-not-experience-issues-due-to-conflicting-stakeholders-needs&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#66-the-program-manager-updates-the-stakeholders-register-and-sends-the-program-scope-statement-to-the-legal-adviser-for-review-the-legal-adviser-recommends-several-changes-the-program-manager-meets-with-stakeholders-from-marketing-finance-and-operations-to-discuss-the-changes-and-obtain-approvals-these-stakeholders-believe-that-the-changes-will-diminish-the-products-value-and-affect-profitability-what-must-be-updated-and-acted-upon-to-ensure-the-program-does-not-experience-issues-due-to-conflicting-stakeholders-needs&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 66. The program manager updates the stakeholders’ register and sends the program scope statement to the legal adviser for review. The legal adviser recommends several changes. The program manager meets with stakeholders from marketing, finance, and operations to discuss the changes and obtain approvals. These stakeholders believe that the changes will diminish the product’s value and affect profitability. What must be updated and acted upon to ensure the program does not experience issues due to conflicting stakeholders’ needs?&lt;/h4&gt;
