&lt;h4 id=&#34;75-a-program-manager-is-identifying-and-verifying-risk-as-outlined-in-the-risk-management-plan-the-results-will-be-recorded-in-which-of-the-following&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#75-a-program-manager-is-identifying-and-verifying-risk-as-outlined-in-the-risk-management-plan-the-results-will-be-recorded-in-which-of-the-following&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 75. A program manager is identifying and verifying risk as outlined in the risk management plan. The results will be recorded in which of the following?&lt;/h4&gt;
