&lt;h4 id=&#34;146-when-initiate-the-program-during-developing-program-financial-plan-what-should-be-done-to-reflect-the-environment-change&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#146-when-initiate-the-program-during-developing-program-financial-plan-what-should-be-done-to-reflect-the-environment-change&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 146. When initiate the program, during developing program financial plan what should be done to reflect the environment change?&lt;/h4&gt;
