&lt;h4 id=&#34;68-which-of-the-following-items-are-key-elements-of-the-program-charter&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#68-which-of-the-following-items-are-key-elements-of-the-program-charter&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 68. Which of the following items are key elements of the program charter?&lt;/h4&gt;
