&lt;h4 id=&#34;170-at-the-start-of-the-program-to-assure-a-common-understanding-of-program-scope-among-all-stakeholders-for-program-success-which-document-provides-an-understanding-of-the-program-scope&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#170-at-the-start-of-the-program-to-assure-a-common-understanding-of-program-scope-among-all-stakeholders-for-program-success-which-document-provides-an-understanding-of-the-program-scope&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 170. At the start of the program, to assure a common understanding of program scope among all stakeholders for program success, which document provides an understanding of the program scope?&lt;/h4&gt;
