&lt;h4 id=&#34;16-in-program-delivery-phase-you-received-an-email-from-ceo-asking-for-accelerating-the-program-delivery-to-catch-a-market-window-that-will-have-impact-on-three-component-projects-abc-to-meet-the-market-change-what-should-you-do-in-next-step&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#16-in-program-delivery-phase-you-received-an-email-from-ceo-asking-for-accelerating-the-program-delivery-to-catch-a-market-window-that-will-have-impact-on-three-component-projects-abc-to-meet-the-market-change-what-should-you-do-in-next-step&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 16. In program delivery phase, you received an email from CEO asking for accelerating the program delivery to catch a market window, that will have impact on three component projects A,B,C to meet the market change. What should you do in next step?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A. Ask project A, B, C to speed up the schedule&lt;br /&gt;
