&lt;h4 id=&#34;31-portfolio-manager-proposes-a-new-product-that-is-expected-to-be-initiated-the-program-business-case-shows-that-the-new-program-meets-the-portfolio-roi-and-npv-targets-what-is-the-next-document-the-program-manager-should-develop&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#31-portfolio-manager-proposes-a-new-product-that-is-expected-to-be-initiated-the-program-business-case-shows-that-the-new-program-meets-the-portfolio-roi-and-npv-targets-what-is-the-next-document-the-program-manager-should-develop&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 31. Portfolio manager proposes a new product that is expected to be initiated. The program business case shows that the new program meets the portfolio ROI and NPV targets. What is the next document the program manager should develop?&lt;/h4&gt;
