&lt;h4 id=&#34;32-a-company-wants-to-perform-a-preliminary-stakeholder-analysis-to-assess-a-new-programs-support-what-should-the-program-manager-develop&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#32-a-company-wants-to-perform-a-preliminary-stakeholder-analysis-to-assess-a-new-programs-support-what-should-the-program-manager-develop&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 32. A company wants to perform a preliminary stakeholder analysis to assess a new program’s support. What should the program manager develop?&lt;/h4&gt;
