&lt;h4 id=&#34;39-there-are-four-projects-in-a-program-according-to-following-information-which-project-will-be-canceled-based-on-roi-at-the-next-phase-gate-review-meeting&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#39-there-are-four-projects-in-a-program-according-to-following-information-which-project-will-be-canceled-based-on-roi-at-the-next-phase-gate-review-meeting&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 39. There are four projects in a program. According to following information, which project will be canceled based on ROI at the next phase-gate review meeting?&lt;/h4&gt;
