&lt;h4 id=&#34;40-macro-is-suffering-from-low-participation-from-the-stakeholder-in-his-program-he-wants-to-identify-potential-risks-cause-by-a-lack-of-participation-from-stakeholders-what-should-he-do&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#40-macro-is-suffering-from-low-participation-from-the-stakeholder-in-his-program-he-wants-to-identify-potential-risks-cause-by-a-lack-of-participation-from-stakeholders-what-should-he-do&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 40. Macro is suffering from low participation from the stakeholder in his program. He wants to identify potential risks cause by a lack of participation from stakeholders. What should he do?&lt;/h4&gt;
