&lt;h4 id=&#34;82-the-program-is-consisted-of-several-component-projectsand-all-project-are-scheduled-to-completed-on-the-december-31st-a-mandatory-change-happened-which-would-delay-the-program-schedule-what-action-should-the-program-take-to-deal-the-situation&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#82-the-program-is-consisted-of-several-component-projectsand-all-project-are-scheduled-to-completed-on-the-december-31st-a-mandatory-change-happened-which-would-delay-the-program-schedule-what-action-should-the-program-take-to-deal-the-situation&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 82. The Program is consisted of several component projects,and all project are scheduled to completed on the December 31st. A mandatory change happened which would delay the program schedule, what action should the program take to deal the situation?&lt;/h4&gt;
