&lt;h4 id=&#34;83-a-program-manager-was-charged-an-on-going-program-the-previous-manager-make-alienated-and-angry-with-the-clients-the-staff-dont-compliance-with-organization-policies-and-have-no-action-in-program-and-program-activities-what-can-program-manager-do-next&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#83-a-program-manager-was-charged-an-on-going-program-the-previous-manager-make-alienated-and-angry-with-the-clients-the-staff-dont-compliance-with-organization-policies-and-have-no-action-in-program-and-program-activities-what-can-program-manager-do-next&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 83. A program manager was charged an on-going program. The previous manager make alienated and angry with the clients. The staff don’t compliance with organization policies and have no action in program and program activities. What can program manager do next?&lt;/h4&gt;
