&lt;h4 id=&#34;107-a-company-does-a-new-system-the-program-change-management-team-conduct-a-training-to-the-employees-on-the-new-system-during-the-meeting-the-employee-felt-too-much-on-the-change-and-workload-will-increase-they-walkout-the-room-what-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#107-a-company-does-a-new-system-the-program-change-management-team-conduct-a-training-to-the-employees-on-the-new-system-during-the-meeting-the-employee-felt-too-much-on-the-change-and-workload-will-increase-they-walkout-the-room-what-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 107. A company does a new system, the program change management team conduct a training to the employees on the new system, during the meeting, the employee felt too much on the change, and workload will increase, they walkout the room, what program manager do?&lt;/h4&gt;
