&lt;h4 id=&#34;110-a-program-manager-is-working-on-benefits-the-program-team-created-and-updated-a-benefits-register-earlier-in-the-program-the-benefits-register-should-include-which-of-the-following&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#110-a-program-manager-is-working-on-benefits-the-program-team-created-and-updated-a-benefits-register-earlier-in-the-program-the-benefits-register-should-include-which-of-the-following&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 110. A program manager is working on benefits. The program team created and updated a benefits register earlier in the program. The benefits register should include which of the following?&lt;/h4&gt;
