 D. 项目集进度表&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;113-a-program-stakeholder-is-concerned-about-information-he-received-about-a-project-who-is-responsible-for-reviewing-the-communications-management-plan-to-assure-adequate-information-is-provided-to-the-stakeholder&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#113-a-program-stakeholder-is-concerned-about-information-he-received-about-a-project-who-is-responsible-for-reviewing-the-communications-management-plan-to-assure-adequate-information-is-provided-to-the-stakeholder&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 113. A program stakeholder is concerned about information he received about a project. Who is responsible for reviewing the communications management plan to assure adequate information is provided to the stakeholder?&lt;/h4&gt;
