&lt;h4 id=&#34;114-during-the-program-execution-stage-the-component-project-manager-responsible-for-testing-estimates-that-budgeted-hours-may-exceed-200-hours-what-should-the-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#114-during-the-program-execution-stage-the-component-project-manager-responsible-for-testing-estimates-that-budgeted-hours-may-exceed-200-hours-what-should-the-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 114. During the program execution stage, the component project manager responsible for testing estimates that budgeted hours may exceed 200 hours. What should the program manager do?&lt;/h4&gt;
