&lt;h4 id=&#34;115-your-company-has-decided-to-regroup-four-existing-projects-and-manage-them-as-a-program-you-have-just-been-assigned-as-the-program-manager-for-historical-reasons-each-existing-project-has-its-own-project-management-information-system-pmis-project-managers-have-a-lot-of-experience-in-their-domain-of-responsibility-and-their-pmis-have-an-excellent-reputation-in-the-company-your-company-has-ask-you-develop-a-dedicate-pmis-used-to-your-program-and-you-are-wonder-who-are-contribute-to-pmis-assets-what-is-the-best-option-to-answer-this-question&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#115-your-company-has-decided-to-regroup-four-existing-projects-and-manage-them-as-a-program-you-have-just-been-assigned-as-the-program-manager-for-historical-reasons-each-existing-project-has-its-own-project-management-information-system-pmis-project-managers-have-a-lot-of-experience-in-their-domain-of-responsibility-and-their-pmis-have-an-excellent-reputation-in-the-company-your-company-has-ask-you-develop-a-dedicate-pmis-used-to-your-program-and-you-are-wonder-who-are-contribute-to-pmis-assets-what-is-the-best-option-to-answer-this-question&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 115. Your company has decided to regroup four existing projects and manage them as a program. You have just been assigned as the program manager. For historical reasons, each existing project has its own Project Management Information System (PMIS). Project managers have a lot of experience in their domain of responsibility, and their PMIS have an excellent reputation in the company. Your company has ask you develop a dedicate PMIS used to your program. And you are wonder who are contribute to PMIS assets. What is the BEST option to answer this question?&lt;/h4&gt;
