&lt;h4 id=&#34;116-the-flx-program-is-very-critical-to-good-day-organization-during-the-program-kick-off-meeting-some-stakeholders-stressed-that-they-need-to-assess-the-overall-health-of-the-program-and-take-appropriate-action-to-ensure-successful-benefits-delivery-what-is-the-most-important-action-that-should-be-done-by-the-program-manager-to-fulfill-this-request&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#116-the-flx-program-is-very-critical-to-good-day-organization-during-the-program-kick-off-meeting-some-stakeholders-stressed-that-they-need-to-assess-the-overall-health-of-the-program-and-take-appropriate-action-to-ensure-successful-benefits-delivery-what-is-the-most-important-action-that-should-be-done-by-the-program-manager-to-fulfill-this-request&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 116. The FLX program is very critical to Good Day organization. During the program kick-off meeting, some stakeholders stressed that they need to assess the overall health of the program and take appropriate action to ensure successful benefits delivery. What is the most important action that should be done by the program manager to fulfill this request?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A. The program manager should refine program benefits risks&lt;br /&gt;
