&lt;h4 id=&#34;134-a-project-is-assigned-to-a-qualified-project-manager-by-the-program-manager-the-client-rejects-the-project-manager-due-to-a-lack-of-proper-qualifications-to-manage-such-a-project-what-should-the-program-manager-do-next&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#134-a-project-is-assigned-to-a-qualified-project-manager-by-the-program-manager-the-client-rejects-the-project-manager-due-to-a-lack-of-proper-qualifications-to-manage-such-a-project-what-should-the-program-manager-do-next&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 134. A project is assigned to a qualified project manager by the program manager. The client rejects the project manager due to a lack of proper qualifications to manage such a project. What should the program manager do next?&lt;/h4&gt;
