&lt;h4 id=&#34;135-during-the-last-steering-committee-meeting-a-program-manager-presented-the-benefits-register-to-the-program-governance-board-since-the-intended-benefits-of-the-program-were-realized-the-program-manager-was-asked-to-transition-the-program-into-operations-at-this-stage-what-is-expected-during-the-post-review-session-organized-by-the-program-manager&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#135-during-the-last-steering-committee-meeting-a-program-manager-presented-the-benefits-register-to-the-program-governance-board-since-the-intended-benefits-of-the-program-were-realized-the-program-manager-was-asked-to-transition-the-program-into-operations-at-this-stage-what-is-expected-during-the-post-review-session-organized-by-the-program-manager&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 135. During the last steering committee meeting, a program manager presented the benefits register to the program governance board. Since the intended benefits of the program were realized, the program manager was asked to transition the program into operations. At this stage, what is expected during the post-review session organized by the program manager?&lt;/h4&gt;
