&lt;h4 id=&#34;136-the-program-manager-completed-the-programs-benefits-analysis-and-planning-activities-what-will-this-ensure-for-the-program&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#136-the-program-manager-completed-the-programs-benefits-analysis-and-planning-activities-what-will-this-ensure-for-the-program&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 136. The program manager completed the program’s benefits analysis and planning activities. What will this ensure for the program?&lt;/h4&gt;
