&lt;h4 id=&#34;165-a-program-manager-defines-a-new-program-with-great-potential-benefits-for-the-organization-which-has-experienced-both-successes-and-failures-in-preparation-for-program-initiation-what-should-the-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#165-a-program-manager-defines-a-new-program-with-great-potential-benefits-for-the-organization-which-has-experienced-both-successes-and-failures-in-preparation-for-program-initiation-what-should-the-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 165. A program manager defines a new program with great potential benefits for the organization which has experienced both successes and failures. In preparation for program initiation. What should the program manager do?&lt;/h4&gt;
