 B. 项目经理&lt;br /&gt;
 C. 项目集发起人&lt;br /&gt;
 D. 职能经理&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;167-the-program-manager-wants-to-increase-the-teams-commitment-to-the-program-objectives-the-program-manager-should-do-which-of-the-following&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#167-the-program-manager-wants-to-increase-the-teams-commitment-to-the-program-objectives-the-program-manager-should-do-which-of-the-following&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 167. The program manager wants to increase the team’s commitment to the program objectives. The program manager should do which of the following?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A. Work with the sponsor to identify the organization’s best practices.&lt;br /&gt;
