&lt;h4 id=&#34;14-you-as-program-manager-is-performing-benefit-analysis-and-planning-what-can-get-from-this-activity-as-a-foundation-to-ensure-program-benefits-delivery&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#14-you-as-program-manager-is-performing-benefit-analysis-and-planning-what-can-get-from-this-activity-as-a-foundation-to-ensure-program-benefits-delivery&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 14. You as program manager is performing benefit analysis and planning. What can get from this activity as a foundation to ensure program benefits delivery?&lt;/h4&gt;
