&lt;h4 id=&#34;19-a-company-decides-to-expand-its-business-into-new-market-this-required-the-initiation-of-a-new-program-to-take-the-program-with-ambitious-goals-the-program-manger-prepared-the-business-case-and-received-an-authorization-from-the-organizations-leadership-what-is-the-next-step-the-program-manger-must-take&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#19-a-company-decides-to-expand-its-business-into-new-market-this-required-the-initiation-of-a-new-program-to-take-the-program-with-ambitious-goals-the-program-manger-prepared-the-business-case-and-received-an-authorization-from-the-organizations-leadership-what-is-the-next-step-the-program-manger-must-take&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 19. A company decides to expand its business into new market this required the initiation of a new program to take the program with ambitious goals. The program manger prepared the business case and received an authorization from the organizations leadership. What is the next step the program manger must take?&lt;/h4&gt;
