&lt;h4 id=&#34;55-the-program-manager-is-concerned-the-program-scope-cannot-be-met-with-the-available-internal-and-external-resource-how-should-the-program-manager-evaluate-these-concerns&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#55-the-program-manager-is-concerned-the-program-scope-cannot-be-met-with-the-available-internal-and-external-resource-how-should-the-program-manager-evaluate-these-concerns&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 55. The program manager is concerned the program scope cannot be met with the available internal and external resource. How should the program manager evaluate these concerns?&lt;/h4&gt;
