&lt;h4 id=&#34;56-cindy-the-program-manager-in-hopton-organization-started-to-quantify-all-benefits-added-to-the-benefits-register-why-are-benefits-quantified&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#56-cindy-the-program-manager-in-hopton-organization-started-to-quantify-all-benefits-added-to-the-benefits-register-why-are-benefits-quantified&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 56. Cindy, the program manager in Hopton organization, started to quantify all benefits added to the benefits register. Why are benefits quantified?&lt;/h4&gt;
