 D. 修订项目集时间表，以适应收益的加速交付，并将其提交给指导委员会批准&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;58-you-are-managing-a-program-which-contains-six-components-at-the-end-of-this-year-during-the-benefit-delivery-phase-you-present-the-program-status-to-the-stakeholders-and-the-sponsor-the-program-have-competed-30-of-its-work-but-the-stakeholders-worry-that-expected-benefits-will-not-materialize-which-document-contains-the-key-performance-indicators-and-procedures-to-measure-the-progress&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#58-you-are-managing-a-program-which-contains-six-components-at-the-end-of-this-year-during-the-benefit-delivery-phase-you-present-the-program-status-to-the-stakeholders-and-the-sponsor-the-program-have-competed-30-of-its-work-but-the-stakeholders-worry-that-expected-benefits-will-not-materialize-which-document-contains-the-key-performance-indicators-and-procedures-to-measure-the-progress&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 58. You are managing a program which contains six components. At the end of this year during the benefit delivery phase, you present the program status to the stakeholders and the sponsor, the program have competed 30% of its work, but the stakeholders worry that expected benefits will not materialize. Which document contains the key performance indicators and procedures to measure the progress?&lt;/h4&gt;
