&lt;h4 id=&#34;59-the-program-manager-works-with-a-global-program-team-what-should-the-program-manager-do-to-acknowledge-the-teams-customs-and-cultures&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#59-the-program-manager-works-with-a-global-program-team-what-should-the-program-manager-do-to-acknowledge-the-teams-customs-and-cultures&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 59. The program manager works with a global program team. What should the program manager do to acknowledge the team’s customs and cultures?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A. Conduct a sensitivity training for the team to develop an understanding of the cultures and customs of the team.&lt;br /&gt;
B. Work with the program team to update the communication management plan.&lt;br /&gt;
C. Adjust the communications plan to identify the multiple language of the contractors that are part of the team.&lt;br /&gt;
