&lt;h4 id=&#34;86-bob-is-a-program-manager-he-has-started-working-on-a-new-program-he-is-currently-documenting-why-the-program-is-important-as-well-as-what-the-program-should-achieve-what-is-bob-working-on&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#86-bob-is-a-program-manager-he-has-started-working-on-a-new-program-he-is-currently-documenting-why-the-program-is-important-as-well-as-what-the-program-should-achieve-what-is-bob-working-on&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 86. Bob is a program manager. He has started working on a new program. He is currently documenting why the program is important as well as what the program should achieve. What is Bob working on?&lt;/h4&gt;
