&lt;h4 id=&#34;111-the-program-manager-plans-to-address-a-negative-cost-variance-generating-a-red-flag-in-the-program-management-status-report-what-should-the-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#111-the-program-manager-plans-to-address-a-negative-cost-variance-generating-a-red-flag-in-the-program-management-status-report-what-should-the-program-manager-do&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 111. The program manager plans to address a negative cost variance generating a red flag in the program management status report. What should the program manager do?&lt;/h4&gt;
