&lt;h4 id=&#34;122-program-manager-begins-mapping-defining-identifying-unifying-coordinating-various-program-components-what-program-management-activity-are-being-executed&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#122-program-manager-begins-mapping-defining-identifying-unifying-coordinating-various-program-components-what-program-management-activity-are-being-executed&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 122. Program manager begins mapping, defining, identifying, unifying, coordinating various program components. What program management activity are being executed?&lt;/h4&gt;
