 C. 要求项目集的业务分析师收集所有项目信息并创建报告&lt;br /&gt;
 D. 确保所有项目集文件，包括经验教训，都存档在知识库中&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;161-in-which-subphase-the-program-manager-is-assigned&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#161-in-which-subphase-the-program-manager-is-assigned&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 161. In which subphase the program manager is assigned?&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A. Definition&lt;br /&gt;
