C. Revise the project schedules to meet the program schedule and communicate to stakeholders.&lt;br /&gt;
D. Integrate the project schedules into the program schedule and report the revised delivery date to the project managers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; 　组织必须加快产品推向市场。项目集经理完成初步的项目集时间表步骤并召开启动会议。项目经理也提交了他们的时间表以便进行评审。项目集经理接下来应该做什么？&lt;/p&gt;
